## Technologies Used

This project was implemented using the following technologies:

- Java
- Apache Maven
- JUnit
- Visual Studio Code

## Building the Project

Before building the project, ensure that Java and Maven are installed and configured correctly.

To compile the project and create the executable JAR file, execute:


mvn clean package


To generate the project documentation and reports, execute:


mvn clean package site assembly:single


## Running the Application

After successfully building the project, run the application using:


java -jar target/BinaryCalculator-1.0.0.jar


The program displays the results of the implemented binary operations.

## Running Unit Tests

JUnit test cases are included to verify the correctness of the Binary class methods.

To execute all tests, run:


mvn test


If all tests pass successfully, Maven displays a BUILD SUCCESS message.

## Assignment Requirements

This project satisfies the design requirements by implementing additional binary operations including OR, AND, and Multiplication. The application was updated to demonstrate these new functions, and corresponding JUnit test cases were added to validate their correctness.

